OL,3,CInfected blood scandal: Hunt set to
OL,4,Cunveil #10 billion compensation package
OL,6,FAfter seven years, the findings of a
OL,7,Freport into one of the biggest
OL,8,Fscandals the NHS has ever faced are
OL,9,Fdue to be published next week, as ITV
OL,10,FNews Presenter Alex Iszatt reports
OL,12,FJeremy Hunt is expected to unveil a
OL,13,F#10 billion compensation package for
OL,14,Fvictims of the infected blood scandal.
OL,16,FThe chancellor said he was fulfilling
OL,17,Fa promise he made to a constituent in
OL,18,F2014 just months before he died of
OL,19,Fhepatitis C after being given
OL,20,Fcontaminated blood products.
