OL,3,CInfected blood scandal: Hunt set to
OL,4,Cunveil #10 billion compensation package
OL,6,FTens of thousands of people were
OL,7,Finfected with contaminated blood or
OL,8,Fblood products between the 1970s and
OL,9,Fearly 1990s.
OL,11,FThe scandal ` dubbed the worst
OL,12,Ftreatment disaster in the history of
OL,13,Fthe NHS ` has been the subject of the
OL,14,Fbiggest ever public inquiry in the UK.
OL,16,FDeclaring a compensation package for
OL,17,Fvictims in an interview in The Sunday
OL,18,FTimes, Mr Hunt told of how he promised
OL,19,Fto "sort" a fair and full settlement
OL,20,Fduring a meeting with campaigner Mike
OL,21,FDorricott in 2014.
