OL,6,FDefence Secretary Grant Shapps tells
OL,7,FITV News victims should have had
OL,8,Fdetails of report 'a very long time
OL,9,Fago' as he decries 'absolute scandal'
OL,10,Fthat has 'gone on for decades'
OL,12,FMr Dorricott was 46 at the time, and
OL,13,Fhad learned just weeks before meeting
OL,14,FMr Hunt that he had terminal liver
OL,15,Fcancer ` a disease linked to the
OL,16,Fhepatitis C he contracted as a
OL,17,Fteenager from contaminated Factor 8
OL,18,Fblood products.
