OL,3,CInfected blood scandal: Hunt set to
OL,4,Cunveil #10 billion compensation package
OL,6,FMr Hunt told The that a new
OL,7,Fcompensation package of at least #10
OL,8,Fbillion for those affected by the
OL,9,Fscandal will be "thanks to Mike more
OL,10,Fthan anyone else".
OL,12,FHe added: And it's one of the saddest
OL,13,Fthings that he's not around to see it."
OL,15,FThe chancellor told the paper that Mr
OL,16,FDorricott was "so gentle, so decent".
OL,17,FHe added: "I imagine after that
OL,18,Fmeeting that Mike thought that he'd
OL,19,Fbeen fobbed off by yet another
OL,20,Fpolitician giving him the runaround.
