OL,3,CInfected blood scandal: Hunt set to
OL,4,Cunveil #10 billion compensation package
OL,6,F"But what Mike didn't know was that he
OL,7,Freally had made a huge impression on
OL,8,Fme."
OL,10,FMr Hunt said the money will be funded
OL,11,Fthrough government borrowing, and that
OL,12,Fthe package could be unveiled as soon
OL,13,Fas Tuesday ` one day after the final
OL,14,Freport of the inquiry is due to be
OL,15,Fpublished.
OL,17,FHe said the government would look
OL,18,F"very sympathetically" on any request
OL,19,Ffrom the victims or families for a
OL,20,Fnational memorial.
