OL,3,CInfected blood scandal: Hunt set to
OL,4,Cunveil #10 billion compensation package
OL,6,F"What we want to do after Monday is
OL,7,Fvery close engagement with all the
OL,8,Ffamilies who've been through such hell
OL,9,Fand understand from them what the next
OL,10,Fsteps need to be," he said.
OL,12,FIn an op-ed for the , Labour leader
OL,13,FSir Keir Starmer has also vowed a
OL,14,Fcompensation package if he wins the
OL,15,Fnext general election.
OL,17,FMr Dorricott's widow, Ann, 57, told
OL,18,Fthe paper that the announcement
OL,19,F"brings me solace".
