OL,3,CInfected blood scandal: Hunt set to
OL,4,Cunveil #10 billion compensation package
OL,6,F"It brings me solace to know that even
OL,7,Fin death, Mike continues to make a
OL,8,Fdifference," she said.
OL,10,F"He was a pillar of strength, fighting
OL,11,Ffor justice until his last breath and
OL,12,Fhis absence is deeply felt every day.
OL,14,F"I know that Mike always held Jeremy
OL,15,FHunt in high regard, and even though
OL,16,Fit has taken 10 years, he would be
OL,17,Fpleased that justice is finally being
OL,18,Fdelivered to the victims."
